Package: fastfocal
Type: Package
Title: Fast Focal and Multi-Scale Raster Operations with Optional FFT
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Ho Yi", "Wan", email = "hoyiwan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Fast moving-window ("focal") and buffered extraction for raster data using 'terra'. 
    Selects between a C++ backend (via 'terra') and a Fast Fourier Transform (FFT) backend 
    automatically based on problem size, with optional padding to FFT-friendly lengths. 
    Supports common window types (e.g., circle, rectangle, gaussian), summary functions 
    (mean, sum, min, max, standard deviation, median), and NA handling consistent with 'terra' 
    via 'na.rm' and 'na.policy'. Operates on 'SpatRaster' objects and returns results 
    with the same geometry.
